This Barcelona front three from the 2021-22 season vs. their current front three this season 😮

Not so long ago, Barça front three was players like Depay, De Jong, Dest, & Braithwaite.. 😳

And now,

Barça’s FRONT THREE have scored the MOST GOALS in Europe’s Top Five Leagues this season! 🔥

🇪🇸 Yamal — 14 goals, 22 assists
🇧🇷 Raphinha — 30 goals, 23 assists
🇵🇱 Lewandowski — 40 goals, 3 assists

A combined total of 84 goals and 48 assists. 😳
